About Mediacom Communications

Mediacom the local cable company that serves more than 1,500 communities across the country. Mediacom is the largest cable company in Iowa and second largest in Illinois. Examples of cities with Mediacom service include Albany, Georgia, Columbus, Georgia, Tifton, Georgia, and Valdosta, Georgia, Ames, Iowa, Cedar Rapids, Iowa and Des Moines, Iowa, Quad Cities on the border between Iowa / Illinois; Columbia, Missouri, Jefferson City, Missouri, and Springfield, Missouri. Mediacom also serves outlying areas of the Gulf Coast of Florida and around Minneapolis, Minnesota.
Mediacom Communications offers three basic services for your home: telephone, Internet and cable TV. The services offered by Mediacom depends on what area you live in. Not all services are available in all areas. Check availability of package deals above. Similarly, not all packages are available in each area.
With the purchase of a package of services from Mediacom, you do not only receive quality multiple services. Mediacom is known for its warmth and quality team of customer service that is always there when help is needed. You're getting a brand you can trust. Mediacom's name is synonymous with quality of communications services.
Better TV, Faster Internet, Smarter Phone.Mediacom Bundles are the latest trend, providing the convenience and the savings consumers once only dreamed about. Think about the ease of having Mediacom High-Speed Internet, Mediacom Digital Voice and Mediacom Cable TV all on one bill.
Getting started is simple! The Mediacom Triple Play offers the hippest features and newest technologies available. Check out and compare the best Mediacom service bundles in your area and then order NOW! Make sure you act fast to get your Cable TV, Internet and Phone service for a special low price.
