            Mediacom Digital Cable TV features more channels, services, packages and
            convenience.
        Digital cable offers clear digital pictures and enhanced sound on a broad array
        of television and commercial-free music channels. Once you have Family Cable, it's
        easy to add-on the digital cable package that's right for you and your family, from
        Star Paks featuring multiple channels of premium networks and On Demand services,
        to new services like HDTV and DVR. There are many more advantages with digital cable
        TV including parental control you can access and manage through your digital remote
        control.
            Mediacom HD Cable
        High-definition television features sharper, wider and more lifelike pictures plus
        clear digital sound. Watch the full-screen versions of movies, see more of the big
        sports play, and experience the true colors and crisp details of landscapes, news
        and travel programs and documentaries. All you need is your high-definition TV set
        and Mediacom’s advanced HD receiver or cable card. No other equipment is
        necessary.
        Mediacom customers who have an HDTV with a digital tuner can receive their
        local broadcasters in HD at no additional charge. Mediacom digital cable
        customers with an advanced HD receiver or cable card, automatically receive the
        HD Family Basic channels at no additional charge. If you subscribe to HBO, Showtime
        or Starz premium services, you also receive their HD channels at no additional charge.
            Mediacom ON DEMAND
        Mediacom ON DEMAND is a service that enables customer access to movies
        and special programs ranging from recently released blockbuster titles to timeless
        classics. With Mediacom ON DEMAND get movies at your fingertips. With HD,
        DVR, and ON DEMAND - Mediacom is the way to go! Get a DVR that allows you
        to pause, rewind, and record live TV. Whatever your entertainment needs may be Mediacom
        Cable TV delivers!
